### Listar todos os bancos
GET {{baseUrl}}/bancos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 200 OK
# {
#   "data": [...],
#   "total": 269
# }

###

### Listar bancos ativos
GET {{baseUrl}}/bancos/ativos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Buscar bancos por termo
GET {{baseUrl}}/bancos/search?q=brasil
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Buscar banco por código FEBRABAN
GET {{baseUrl}}/bancos/codigo/001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Buscar banco por código interno
GET {{baseUrl}}/bancos/codigo-interno/BB
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Buscar banco por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/bancos/{{bancoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 200 OK
# {
#   "id": "uuid",
#   "codigo": "001",
#   "codigo_interno": "BB",
#   "nome": "Banco do Brasil S.A.",
#   "status": "ativo",
#   "descricao": "Banco do Brasil S.A. - Código FEBRABAN: 001",
#   "created_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
#   "updated_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
# }

###

### Criar novo banco
POST {{baseUrl}}/bancos
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "codigo": "999",
  "codigo_interno": "NOVO",
  "nome": "Banco Novo S.A.",
  "website": "https://www.banconovo.com.br",
  "status": "ativo",
  "descricao": "Novo banco digital"
}

### Expected Response
# Status: 201 Created
# {
#   "id": "uuid",
#   "codigo": "999",
#   "codigo_interno": "NOVO",
#   "nome": "Banco Novo S.A.",
#   "website": "https://www.banconovo.com.br",
#   "status": "ativo",
#   "descricao": "Novo banco digital",
#   "created_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
#   "updated_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
# }

###

### Atualizar banco
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bancos/{{bancoId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "website": "https://www.bancobrasil.com.br",
  "descricao": "Banco do Brasil - Atualizado"
}

###

### Alternar status do banco
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bancos/{{bancoId}}/toggle-status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Deletar banco
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/bancos/{{bancoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}